3. ‚úÖ Implement tools in `server/tools/`
4. ‚úÖ Configure StateSchema in `server/types/env.ts`
5. ‚úÖ Write comprehensive README.md
6. ‚úÖ Test locally with `bun run dev`
7. ‚úÖ Run `bun run fmt && bun run lint && bun run check`
8. ‚úÖ Create PR for review

### Pre-Commit Checklist

Before committing, verify:
- [ ] `app.json` exists at root level
- [ ] `app.json` has all required fields (scopeName, name, friendlyName, connection, description, icon)
- [ ] `connection.url` matches pattern: `https://sites-{folder-name}.decocache.com/mcp`
- [ ] `mesh_description` is under 1500 characters
- [ ] Added to `deploy.json`
- [ ] All tools have `[ASYNC]` prefix if async (takes >1 second)
- [ ] README.md documents all tools
- [ ] Code passes `bun run fmt && bun run lint && bun run check`

